      "sceneId": "launch",
      "background": "assets/story/pixel-worlds-v1/scenes/sci-fi/sf-08.webp",
      "lines": [
        {
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "八枚光核在发射台上排成一张星图。地图的另一端，传来森林和方块世界的回声。",
          "character": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "这里就是回家发射台。我们先把“点亮星图”记在地图上。",
          "character": "hero",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "我听到光核在轻轻嗡鸣，信号就在附近。",
          "character": "pet",
          "position": "right"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "先看清蓝色航线，再做一个安全的小动作。",
          "character": "star_engineer",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "activity",
          "activityType": "scan",
          "prompt": "点亮星图中央的回家信标。",
          "character": "pet",
          "position": "right",
          "actions": [
            {
              "label": "点亮回家信标",
              "feedback": "星图展开，森林和地下城都亮了起来。"
            },
            {
              "label": "拍拍小飞船",
              "feedback": "小飞船发出欢呼声，准备穿越星门。"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "小小探险家完成了第一步，点亮回家信标让周围的线索变得清楚起来。",
          "character": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "看！刚才藏起来的线索露出来了。",
          "character": "hero",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "扫描光点后，隐藏的星尘轨迹露出来了。",
          "character": "pet",
          "position": "right"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "把这条轨迹和星图接起来，下一站就会亮起。",
          "character": "star_engineer",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "记住这束光，它会带我们穿过下一段星际航线。",
          "character": "star_engineer",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "第一段旅程结束了，新的世界正在等我们。",
          "character": "narrator",
          "position": "center"
        }
      ],
